                   concentration of the inorganic products dissolved in
                   the sample was measured automatically by colorimetry
                   using a 3-channel Technicon AutoAnalyzer system. A
                   number of pure organic compounds were tested in the
                   concentration range encountered in coastal and open
                   ocean, indicating a high efficiency of the digestion
                   procedure. The recovery range is similar to that
